    • getStars

      public java.lang.String getStars()
      Parses rating float value into string that can be used by JSP pages to represent ratings using stars. "on" denotes a full star, "half" denotes a half star, and "off" denotes no star should be displayed.
      Parameters:
      averageRating - of an album object
      Returns:
      String containing "on", "half" or "off" instructions
